lexa.core.data.config

Class ConfigDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • lexa.core.data.BaseDataSet
      • lexa.core.data.SimpleDataSet
        • lexa.core.data.config.ConfigDataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DataItem>, ConfigObject, DataSet

    public class ConfigDataSet
extends SimpleDataSet
implements ConfigObject
    A DataSet for storing configuration data.
    This is used for loading and parsing configuration items. Once read, the object should be closed to ensure that all items have been read.
    A read only extension of a SimpleDataSet. This will behave in all respects like a data set with the added trace of path within the whole set and checking that all the data has been read when closing.
    This class superceded the Deprecated class ConfigData.
    Since:
    2016-09
    Author:
    William
